FT  03 OCT 92 / Beer production
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
BEER production in July of 3.45m barrels was 2.6 per cent higher than a year
before, the Brewers' Society reported yesterday. Production during the 12
months to July, however, was 1.5 per cent less than in the comparable period
a year earlier.
