The supplier, GB Mailing Systems was incorporated in the UK in December
1989, and started trading October 1990. Its turnover in 190-91 was Pounds
500,000. The company has 26 employees.
With the Royal Mail's support, GB Mailing Systems have developed a broad
rage of innovative postcode-based marketing database systems, using the
