Losses per share jumped to 104.7p (56.3p). An extraordinary charge of Pounds
78,000 related to costs of the capital restructuring.
Shareholders will be offered three new shares for every two held, at 25p
apiece. Payment is in two instalments, with 10p due on acceptance and the
balance by next March.
The shares fell 1p to 21p yesterday.
