<TEXT>
TEN pilot 'one-stop shops' will be set up next year to co-ordinate advice to
businesses, Baroness Denton, minister responsible for small businesses,
announced yesterday. The 10 will be the first of a national network of 200
to be set up over the next few years.
So many organisations offered services to business that the owner or manager
